General.Name: Shenzhen Jiang and Associates Creative Design Co Ltd
General.Description: Shenzhen Jiang&Associates Creative Design Co., Ltd. operates as an interior design company in China. The company provides general, architectural, interior, electromechanical, furnishing, and guiding signage design services. It offers commercial space, office space, real estate space, rail transit, hotel space, health care space, public venues, and cultural and education design services. Shenzhen Jiang&Associates Creative Design Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.
